{"id":975,"date":"2011-08-04T08:23:59","date_gmt":"2011-08-04T12:23:59","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=975"},"modified":"2025-04-22T11:56:44","modified_gmt":"2025-04-22T07:56:44","slug":"many-gates-to-enter-paradise","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/08\/04\/many-gates-to-enter-paradise\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Jannah: Many gates through which to enter Paradise"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<b>Anyone who spends a pair in the way of Allah will be called from all the gates of Paradise: O servant of Allah, this is good! The people of prayer will be called from the gate of prayer, the people of jihad will be called from the gate of jihad, the people of fasting will be called from the gate of <\/b><strong>al-Rayyan<\/strong><b>, and the people of charity will be called from the gate of charity.<\/b>\u201d Abu Bakr said, \u201cOne who is called from all those gates would\u00a0need nothing. Will anyone be called from all those gates, O Messenger of Allah?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Yes, and I hope you will be among them, O Abu Bakr<\/strong>.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3666, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1027<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em><strong>Muttafaqun\u00a0<\/strong><\/em><em><strong>Alayhi<\/strong><\/em> (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0